# core.autocrlf is true on this machine. Git sniffs file types by content, and the sample
# takeoff PDFs contain no early NUL bytes — so git misclassified them as TEXT and would have
# applied LF->CRLF conversion, corrupting every downloadable sample on the live site.
# Mark every binary asset explicitly. Do not remove.
*.pdf   binary
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.webp  binary
*.ico   binary

# Keep the site's own source normalised.
*.html  text eol=lf
*.xml   text eol=lf
*.txt   text eol=lf
CNAME   text eol=lf
